{
  "stem": "23438.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "There was also a story about a great-great grandmother who sat in the marketplace at Suwalki, near Wilno, selling love potion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "So the family was quite extensive, as I said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And we spent quite a bit of time together, even though three of the sisters lived in Warsaw and one in [?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "Lodz, ?] what we used to visit each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "All the tradition I knew as a young child was my grandmother's Passover dinner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "It was not really a traditional dinner but just, more or less, a family gathering.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "We were all there that day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I grew up in absolute ignorance of my origin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I just-- I guess my parents did not think it important enough to tell me that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "There was no religion at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "We had a nanny who used to take me, sometimes, to the church.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "But that meant nothing to me, at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And not until I went to school, aged seven, and I was asked the question, what's my religion?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a question you had to answer in Poland in those times, wherever you went, in any documents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, I have no religion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the teacher ask again, what is your religion?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, no madam.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have no religion.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, then, you must be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came home in tears.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mommy, is it true that I am Jewish?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They told me this at school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think they hurt me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Other than that, my childhood was quite a normal, happy childhood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was an employee of the Warsaw agency of Michelin Tires.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a French company.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
